query: query ListBookings($filter: ModelBookingFilterInput, $limit: Int, $nextToken: String) {  listBookings(filter: $filter, limit: $limit, nextToken: $nextToken) {    items {      id      status      bookingReference      outboundFlight {        id        departureDate        departureAirportCode        departureAirportName        departureCity        departureLocale        arrivalDate        arrivalAirportCode        arrivalAirportName        arrivalCity        arrivalLocale        ticketPrice        ticketCurrency        flightNumber      }      checkedIn      createdAt    }    nextToken  }}
